<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-7" id="about">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <img class="img-thumbnail pull-left" src="/images/demenchuk.jpg" style="margin-right: 20px;"/>  
        
        <p class="lead">I'm a <%= Time.now.year - 1988 %> years old full-stack software engineer from Russia, based in Lonon, UK.</p>
        <p class="lead">I carefully craft modern web and mobile applications with PHP, Ruby and JavaScript.</p>
        <p class="lead">I built my first app at the age of eleven and have been pushing myself and my limits ever since.</p>
        <p class="lead">I graduated with a Computer Science degree in 2011 from <a href="http://inter.omgtu.ru">Omsk State Technical University</a>.</p>
        <p class="lead">In my spare time I brew beer.</p>

        <ul class="list-inline text-center">
          <li><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logos/php.png" title="PHP" width="120"/></li>
          <li><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logos/ruby.png" title="Ruby" width="80"/></li>
          <li><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logos/javascript.png" title="Java Script" width="80"/></li>
          <li><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logos/drupal.png" title="Drupal" width="80"/></li>
          <li><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logos/rails.png" title="Ruby on Rails" width="80"/></li>
          <li><img class="img-responsive" src="/images/logos/angularjs.png" title="AngularJS" width="80"/></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-5">
    <%= render :'partials/social' %>
    <p class="lead">If you've found my work particularly useful and want to say <strong>thank you</strong>, there's a wide range of stuff I'd welcome on my wish list (<a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/registry/wishlist/17E9ZXK45NTTU">UK</a>) (<a href="http://amzn.com/w/Q4VIZVMOL8OG">US</a>).</p>
  </div>

</div>

